title: 1.14.4 fabric 在vscode中没有生成源代码只有声明代码
author: 墨之永恒

replies.author: 3TUSK
replies.txt_content:
If you want to browse the source of minecraft you can use the genSources task from gradle, this can be done by running the following command in your terminal .\gradlew genSources.
摘自 https://fabricmc.net/wiki/tutorial:vscode_setup。

注：如果你是 macOS/Linux 用户，那么你用的应该是 ./gradlew 而不是 .\gradlew。
